tags: Treatment satisfaction,
review:
Visted for my scaling work and also for my wife dent cap fitting.

There is scope to improve by front desk support team i.e update to customer about the status of cap arrival and suitable for fixing/appointments. In our case we need to chase them for updates with front desk team.

For treatment satisfaction, doctor advised to follow before and after treatment pics i e in my case before scaling and after scaling pics. Customer will get to know about his bad maintenance of his scaling and after pic (after scaling) will get satisfaction of scaling work

Dr. Anil Kumar did excellent work of filling my chipped tooth with composite resin filling. He was very thorough and professional. I am very happy and grateful to him and his staff for providing great dental service.
Dental office has advanced equipment and is very clean and hygienic.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Dr.Anil was very friendly and he explained the procedure and have completed the procedure smoothly. 

Staff and reception team were very polite and have good knowledge on the medication and procedures. 

The hospital is well maintained and patients wellness and well-being is primarily focused.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Wait time,
review: I underwent treatment for cavities and clearance of my teeth which hasn't done for many years,but still the doctor(Dr.Preeti w/o Dr.Anil) went patient dealing with me by explaining what actually happened and what can be done to prevent it.I am satisfied with the treatment I received and I have to wait for 2 or 3 days to know how the treatment will react on my teeth.Also the staff was very welcoming and supportive.I hope the same rapo continues with them.
